Introduction

Lee Sooyoung is a South Korean singer.

She was a contestant on the JTBC survival show Girls On Fire where she ended up ranking #3 which made her a part of the final group on June 25, 2024.

However, on December 23, 2024, it was announced that the debut of the final group had been canceled.
